## Color Palette

- **Bullish/CALL**: `bg-green-500/10`, `border-green-500/30`, `text-green-500`
- **Bearish/PUT**: `bg-red-500/10`, `border-red-500/30`, `text-red-500`
- **Success/WIN**: `text-green-400`, `bg-green-500/10`
- **Error/LOSE**: `text-red-400`, `bg-red-500/10`
